    "headline": "Ex-AT&T Veteran Jen Asplund Joins MCE Systems’ Advisory Board to Advance Customer Care Growth in North America",
    "summary": "DALLAS, April 27, 2026--MCE Systems, the pioneer of AI-native, digital device lifecycle management (dDLM), today announced the appointment of Jen Asplund, former Vice President of Mobility Customer Care at AT&T, to its Board of Advisors. Asplund will help deepen ties between AT&T and MCE and advise the development of MCE’s expanding roster of telecom customer care solutions with a focus on helping build the value proposition for North America.",
